Class SicretRules

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Observer, toxTree.core.IDecisionMethod, toxTree.core.XMLSerializable
public class SicretRules
extends toxTree.tree.UserDefinedTree

Decision tree for estimating skin irritation and corrosion potential. Implements rules publlished in The Skin Irritation Corrosion Rules Estimation Tool (SICRET), John D. Walker, Ingrid Gerner, Etje Hulzebos, Kerstin Schlegel, QSAR Comb. Sci. 2005, 24, pp378-384.

Rules:

  • physicochemical property limits
  • structural rules
  • implementation in sicret.rules package

Categories:

  • CategoryNotCorrosive
  • CategoryNotIrritatingOrCorrosive
  • CategoryNotIrritating
  • CategoryIrritating
  • CategoryCorrosive
  • CategoryIrritatingOrCorrosive
  • CategoryUnknown

Version:
